{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"188083b814","title":"邀请日共派代表团参加中国国庆的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f5fbb2191a","index":0,"year":1964,"month":9,"day":15,"articleId":"188083b814"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"4290fc8b9a","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"同样内容的邀请信还发给印度尼西亚、泰国、马来亚（今马来西亚）、缅甸、锡兰（今斯里兰卡）等国家的共产党中央委员会和越南劳动党中央委员会。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7766b8ee3d","type":"title","text":"邀请日共派代表团参加中国国庆的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"4290fc8b9a","type":"paragraph","text":"日本共产党中央委员会亲爱的同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"8870e4ce1d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年十月一日是中华人民共和国成立十五周年国庆。中国共产党中央委员会热诚地邀请日本共产党中央委员会派遗代表团前来参加中华人民共和国十五周年国庆典礼","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"9ebf148f52","type":"paragraph","text":"我们深信，日本共产党代表团的光临，将有助于增进我们两党和两国人民之间的战斗友谊和兄弟团结。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"1af1bd919c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们衷心地希望，日本共产党中央委员会接受我们这一邀请。至于代表团人数和由哪一级领导人率领，请你们自己考虑决定。我们希望早日得到关于日本共产党代表团成员的通知","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"c9bb533c7e","type":"subtitle","text":"谨致","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"76dcc3e9b7","type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义的敬礼","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"5d5f69f810","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会主席毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"},{"id":"e13c81b289","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年九月十五日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814"}],"page":{"id":"afcf2465ca","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"188083b814","start":150,"end":150}}}},"__N_SSG":true}